<HL>
   Runway Inflation:
   Travel Is Off, Airlines
   Ailing, but Airports
   Just Keep Expanding
   ---
   Boosterism and Bonds Fuel
   Projects Even as Estimates
   Of Need Are Scaled Back
   ---
   Empty Gates, More Coming
   ----
   By Jonathan Dahl
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/26/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A1
</SO>
