   House Panel
   Votes to Curb
   Insurer Links
   ---
   Antitrust Exemption Tied
   To Joint Actuarial Data
   Threatened by Measure
   ----
   By Paulette Thomas
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
11/20/91
</DATE>
<SO>
